&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;re a hands-on performance marketer who has personally built and managed paid search and Meta campaigns at scale - not directed others to do it. You know what a well-structured Google Ads account looks like because you&#39;ve built one. You know what a broken Meta attribution setup looks like because you&#39;ve fixed one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;re also genuinely excited about what AI tools are doing to this job right now. You&#39;ve used them to move faster, test more, and do work that used to take a week in a day. That&#39;s not a line on your resume - it&#39;s actually how you work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a lean team. You&#39;ll drive impact directly, with ownership of HomeLight&#39;s paid channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll own paid search and paid social for HomeLight - two channels that matter a lot to the business. That means running the campaigns yourself, being accountable for the numbers, and working closely with our data and product teams to ensure we&#39;re measuring correctly.&lt;/p&gt;
